### CLI

Command-line access to the Tuneup functionality.

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///d:/Repo%20Quest%20Log/src/cli/index.ts)
- **New Command:** `repolog tuneup [--write-charter] [--copy] [--agent=claude|codex|gemini]`
  - Prints prompt to stdout.
  - `--write-charter`: Writes to `.repolog/CHARTER.md`.
  - `--copy`: Copies prompt to clipboard using `copyTextToClipboard`.
  - `--agent`: Filters output to the specific `perAgent` string.
- **Modify `doctor` Command:**
  - Update `repolog doctor --json` output to include `tuneup: { score, gapCount }`.

